雄虎跟雌狮的人工圈养混种后代称为[[虎獅|虎獅]]（英语：Tigon），是比狮虎更罕见的混种<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9001344/tigon|title=tigon – Encyclopædia Britannica Article|accessdate=12 September 2007|archive-date=2008-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080410104210/http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9001344/tigon|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

